For armor, the first robe to get is a Flowing Black Robe from Najena in Najena.<br>
Then you have a choice of many other fine robes.<br>
Personally, I am taking it slow, and I am getting all my shadowbound armor right now.<br>
Just go to Everlore.com and look for the shadowbound armor quests given in the <br>
Temple of Solusek.<br>
I think I got that right. =)<br>
For a weapon, I have a dragoon dirk and a Dagger of marnek in my range slot.<br>
Get a Harvester when you can.<p>

