<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">It all depends... When a friend of mine(mage) and me(necro) were doing shadowed men for faction is the temple os solusek ro we both had our pets duelwielding swords of runes which proc a VS summoned spell. Our pets jus ripped through them. It is all preference if you ask me. But if you are going to give ur pet a wep and this is especially important for me at higher levels, make sure it is a magic wep. I usually dont give my pet anything but when I find a magic crappy wep like a gnoll hide lariat Ill give it to my pet. Oh yeah and defiantly start out with an FBR. Then Green Drape or Robe of Enshroudment. After that get whatever you can. I am currently wearing a Kedge Robe(+100 Mana MAGIC LORE NO DROP) and I love it. Good Luck<hr>Blood is like honey... thick and sweet.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
