<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">This is the deal:If the dmg on the weapon is higher then the pets base dmg it will overwrite it. For instance if you give a lvl 7 pet a RTS it will hit for 18 max instead of 14.I am not sure if there is a cap but if there is not a level 1 pet could hit for 24 with a fs 2hander 8). Biggest problem at higher lvl is its not possible to find a reasonably cheap weapon that has more dmg on it then the pets base dmg especially if you are looking for a 1hander cause you want them to dual wield.<hr>minima</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
